messages.title: DO YOU TRUST ED MILIBAND WITH DARLINGTON'S ECONOMY?
messages.content: THE BIGGEST THREAT TO OUR LOCAL ECONOMY IS ED MILIBAND BECOMING PRIME MINISTER. ED MILIBAND'S LABOUR PARTY IS WRONG FOR DARLINGTON.

issues.economy: THE BIGGEST THREAT TO OUR LOCAL ECONOMY IS ED MILIBAND BECOMING PRIME MINISTER.

quotes.text: Ed Miliband's Labour Party is wrong for Darlington.

images.caption: Ed Miliband depicted with text questioning trust in him with Darlington's economy

leaflet.additionalNotes: The leaflet argues that Ed Miliband becoming Prime Minister is a threat to local economy and implies a lack of confidence in his readiness to be Prime Minister, citing public opinion polls.
